OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John Evans
OL,5,FJohn Evans, Age 95, Southampton Docks
OL,7,FInterviewed 24 September 2023
OL,9,FA teenager working at Southampton
OL,10,FDocks, Mr Evans saw ships and landing
OL,11,Fcraft assembling.
OL,13,FHe said: "I was working for a shipping
OL,14,Fcontractor. I was what you call a
OL,15,Fstores assistant. We used to do all of
OL,16,Fthe heavy work, load up the lorries.
OL,18,F"Go out with them and take the stores
OL,19,Faboard ships."
