OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John Evans
OL,5,FHe was doing this work in the lead up
OL,6,Fto the invasion, watching the massive
OL,7,Fbuildup of troops and vehicles - and
OL,8,Fspotted the huge concrete blocks that
OL,9,Fwere to be towed across the Channel to
OL,10,Fmake a harbour.
OL,12,F"We noticed in the harbour all these
OL,13,Fcaissons being built. It was like a
OL,14,Fbig structure and they floated in the
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,F"The Mulberry Harbour, And we saw all
OL,18,Fthe troops, Canadians, Americans and
OL,19,FBritish."
