OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: John Evans
OL,5,FMr Evans arrived at the docks early on
OL,6,F6 June to realise most of the vessels
OL,7,Fhad departed in the night.
OL,9,F"I went into work and I said to the
OL,10,Flads 'I think it's on.' And they said
OL,11,F'What do you mean?' I said 'There is
OL,12,Fvery little noise from the docks.'"
OL,14,FLater he saw the dead and wounded
OL,15,Fbeing brought back through the port,
OL,16,Fas well as German prisoners of war.
